Class OfficerRegistrationRequestDAO

java.lang.Object
BTOManagementSystem.Model.DAO.OfficerRegistrationRequestDAO
public class OfficerRegistrationRequestDAO extends Object
DAO (Data Access Object) class for managing officer registration requests.

Handles creation, retrieval, filtering, updating, and persistence of registration requests for HDB officers who wish to be assigned to BTO projects.
